{"tid":1550841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你班對「香港人權與民主法案」一知半解既人 （2）","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:24:39.000Z","uid":212819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"972021dc3c50117e224adefd68ef3cc11a036571","tid":1550841,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1549246/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1549246/page/1</a><br />\n繼上個post爆左之後 依家再開新post 唔該大家幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋見好多巴打話唔識點用英文講出黎 所以開多左個英文雞精post 幫大家溫下英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">英文雞精post既link</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1550508/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1550508/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPost原文:<br />\n聽日實好撚多外媒喺到 當記者訪問你地問咩係「香港人權與民主法案」時答到口啞啞<br />\n實仲柒過班愛國藍絲廢老<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記住個法案英文係&ldquo;Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act&rdquo;!</span><br />\n用十分鐘睇左下面篇文佢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98-%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598-%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC1Ln0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=643e8d7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598-%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&h=556f1be4\" target=\"_bl